from pyspark.sql.functions import explode, col
df = spark.read.format("json").load("abfss://bronze@imrdatalakedev.dfs.core.windows.net/apiData/apiDatTest.json").withColumn("explodeArray", explode(col("quarterlyReports")))
df.createOrReplaceTempView("myData")

%%sql
SELECT 
    explodeArray.netInterestIncome As InterestIncome,
    explodeArray.fiscalDateEnding As FiscalDate
FROM myData
